%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bundesliga%20Fans%20Protest%20Against%20Private%20Equity%20Investors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17142248%2FGBZ8c1raEAAZip4.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBundesliga%C2%A0and%20Bundesliga%202%20fans%20across%20the%20country%20protested%20on%20Friday%20and%C2%A0Saturday%20against%20the%20German%20Football%20League%E2%80%99s%20(DFL)%20decision%20to%20seek%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20strategic%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%2024%20of%2036%20teams%20between%20the%20two%20divisions%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgreen-light-for-investors-in-german-football%2Fa-67690770%5C%22%3Evoted%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20secure%20private%20equity%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20return%20for%20a%20share%20of%20TV%20rights%20over%20the%20next%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFans%20from%20all%2036%20teams%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbundesliga-deal-what-does-private-equity-want-in-football%2Fa-67732274%5C%22%3Eannounced%20they%20would%20remain%20silent%20for%20the%20first%2012%20minutes%20of%20their%20matches%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0across%20the%20weekend%2C%20with%20multiple%C2%A0matches%20interrupted%20by%20further%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Berlin%20fans%20went%20on%20to%20throw%20tennis%20balls%20and%20chocolate%20coins%20on%20the%20pitch%2C%20forcing%20a%20short%20interruption%20of%20their%20match%20at%20VfL%20Bochum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriker%20Takuma%20Asano%20ate%20one%20of%20the%20chocolate%20coins%20during%20the%20cleanup%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20Bochum%E2%80%99s%20opener%20shortly%20before%20the%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20cause%20injuries%2C%C2%A0serious%20damage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20on%20Friday%20had%20a%20more%20serious%20outcome%2C%20with%C2%A0the%20game%20between%20second%20division%20sides%20Paderborn%20and%20Hansa%20Rostock%20interrupted%20after%20Rostock%20fans%20threw%20pyrotechnics%20onto%20the%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERostock%20fans%20and%20police%20officers%20were%20also%20injured%2C%20and%20there%20was%20an%20estimated%20damage%20of%C2%A0%E2%82%AC100%2C000%20(%24109%2C085)%20reported%20by%20Paderborn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%20eight%20stewards%20and%2012%20police%20officers%20suffered%20injuries%2C%20one%20policewoman%20had%20to%20be%20treated%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20cut%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paderborn%20and%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20enough%20to%20apologize%20and%20distance%20ourselves%2C%20there%20will%20be%20severe%20punishment.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20talk%20about%20clear%20consequences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rostock%20CEO%20Robert%20Marien%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBild%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0newspaper%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Bundesliga%20clash%20between%20Borussia%20M%C3%B6nchengladbach%20and%20Werder%20Bremen%20was%C2%A0%20delayed%20for%20five%20minutes%20after%20fans%20threw%20fake%20coins%20on%20the%20pitch.%20This%20came%20in%20addition%20to%20the%2012%20minutes%20of%C2%A0silence%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20no%20fun%20at%20all%2C%20it%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%C2%A0coronavirus%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bremen%20midfielder%20Leonardo%20Bittencourt%20said%20of%20the%20fans%E2%80%99%20silence%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20games%20played%20with%20no%20paying%20spectators%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DFL%20have%20said%20they%20are%20aiming%20to%20boost%20its%20business%20model%20and%20international%20marketing%20with%20the%20income%20they%20will%20receive%20from%20the%20strategic%20partner%2C%20who%20will%20have%20no%20saying%20in%20sporting%20matters%20such%20as%20fixtures%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbundesliga-fans-protest-against-private-equity-investors%2Fa-67744834%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702803241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbundesliga-fans-protest-against-private-equity-investors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20by%20the%20German%20Football%20League%20to%20allow%20a%20private%20equity%20investor%20for%20the%20next%20two%20decades%20has%20sparked%20backlash%20from%20fans.%20In%20one%20incident%2C%20Hansa%20Rostock%20fans%20threw%20pyrotechnics%2C%20injuring%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Autopsy%20reveals%20Matthew%20Perry's%20agitation%20and%20aggression%20linked%20to%20testosterone%20shots%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20to%20his%20death%3A%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702802902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106062036%2Cimgsize-15318.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fautopsy-reveals-matthew-perrys-agitation-and-aggression-linked-to-testosterone-shots-in-the-weeks-leading-to-his-death-report%2Farticleshow%2F106062036.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106062036.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EWhile%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20Perry%20acquired%20the%20tranquilizer%20ketamine%2C%20a%20female%20associate%20stated%20that%20despite%20irritability%20from%20the%20testosterone%20treatments%2C%20Perry%20seemed%20generally%20happy%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20his%20death.%20The%2029-page%20autopsy%20report%20indicated%20that%20she%20last%20spoke%20to%20him%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20inciden