20Dharavi.%20I%20am%20not%20against%20development%20but%20this%20is%20the%20biggest%20TDR%20%5BTransfer%20of%20Development%20Rights%5D%20scam%20of%20the%20world.%20Adani%20is%20getting%20TDR%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20which%20means%20his%20next%20generations%20can%20also%20live%20peacefully%20without%20working.%20So%20much%20is%20the%20TDR%20that%20the%20government%20is%20gifting%20them.%20But%20we%20will%20not%20let%20that%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fuddhav-dharavi-project-biggest-tdr-scam-9071129%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20to%20redevelop%20Dharavi%20was%20taken%20in%202018%2C%20when%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Therefore%2C%20this%20sin%20is%20of%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Fadnavis%20is%20currently%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20one%20can%20understand%20who%20financed%20the%20toppling%20of%20my%20government.%20With%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20around%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20help%20its%20friends%3B%20so%20my%20party%20was%20broken%20and%20its%20symbol%20was%20stolen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Dharavi%20MLA%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20was%20also%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%20have%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20MVA%20government%20that%20had%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Dharavi%20project%20was%20awarded%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20through%20a%20fair%2C%20open%2C%20internationally%20competitive%20bidding%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20tender%20conditions%20were%20finalised%20during%20the%20MVA%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%