iament%20should%20not%20be%20underestimated%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Speaker%20has%20also%20been%20taking%20necessary%20steps%20with%20all%20seriousness%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-serious-issue-there-should-be-no-squabbling-pm-123121700245_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-serious-issue-there-should-be-no-squabbling-pm-123121700245_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-serious-issue-there-should-be-no-squabbling-pm-123121700245_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20security%20breach%20serious%20issue%2C%20everyone%20should%20avoid%20squabbling%20over%20it%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702797263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106060694%2Cimgsize-2077854.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fparliament-security-breach-serious-issue-everyone-should-avoid-squabbling-over-it-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F106060443.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20first%20remarks%20since%20the%20December%2013%20incident%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20security%20breach%20is%20painful%20and%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20He%20called%20for%20no%20squabbling%20over%20the%20issue%20amid%20the%20opposition's%20protests%20in%20Parliament.%20%26quot%3BEfforts%20should%20also%20be%20made%20to%20look%20for%20a%20solution%20with%20collective%20spirit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20persons%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20and%20sprayed%20yellow%20colour%20smoke%20when%20the%20Zero%20Hour%20proceedings%20were%20going%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVery%20Serious%2C%20We%20Need%20To%20Know%20Who's%20Behind%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Parliament%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20week%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20need%20to%20debate%26quot%3B%20this%20and%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20investigation%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20seriousness%20of%20this%20incident%20should%20not%20be%20downplayed.%20The%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20Speaker%20is%20taking%20all%20the%20necessary%20steps.%20Probe%20agencies%20are%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20find%20out%20which%20elements%20are%20behind%20this%20and%20what%20their%20objectives%20are.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20debate%20this%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20into%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jagran.com%2Fnews%2Fnational-pm-modi-speaks-with-dainik-jagran-on-lok-sabha-security-breach-23606468.html%5C%22%3EDainik%20Jagran%20newspaper%20in%20an%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShocking%20scenes%20played%20out%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20Wednesday%20when%20two%20intruders%20jumped%20from%20desk%20to%20desk%20and%20deployed%20coloured%20smoke%20from%20canisters.%20Their%20co-accused%20staged%20a%20similar%20protest%20outside%20the%20Parliament.%20They%20have%20told%20investigators%20that%20their%20objective%20was%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20unemployment%20and%20farmers'%20problems.%20A%20total%20of%20six%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20so%20far.%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20invoked%20the%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20against%20the%20trespassers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20criticised%20the%20government%20over%20the%20huge%20security%20breach%20and%20demanded%20a%20statement%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20however%2C%20has%20said%20the%20security%20inside%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20under%20the%20secretariat's%20purview%20and%20that%20it%20will%20not%20let%20the%20Centre%20intervene.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20cannot%20intervene%20in%20(responsibilities%20of)%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretariat.%20We%20will%20not%20allow%20that%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20Opposition%20MPs'%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20the%20security%20breach%20is%20a%20serious%20issue.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20asking%20for%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20statement%20in%20Parliament%2C%20but%20the%20Home%20Minister%20is%20not%20saying%20anything%2C%20neither%20is%20he%20giving%20a%20statement.%20He%20is%20speaking%20in%20TV%20shows%2C%20but%20not%20inside%20Parliament.%20This%20is%20not%20good%20for%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20youngsters%20who%20breached%20Parliament's%20security%20were%20youngsters%20who%20are%20jobless%20due%20to%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20policies.%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20is%20that%20of%20unemployment%2C%20which%20is%20boiling%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20The%20country's%20youth%20are%20not%20getting%20employment%20due%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20Modi%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20Mr%20Gandhi%20%26quot%3Balways%20talks%20trash%26quot%3B%20and%20pointing%20out%20that%20unemployment%20was%20at%20its%20lowest%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20I.N.D.I%20Alliance%20leaders%20must%20explain%20the%20close%20linkages%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20Parliament%20breach%20with%20Congress%2C%20TMC%2C%20and%20CPI(M)%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20IT%20in-charge%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702797000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fs80nrod8_pm-parliament-ani_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20week%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20need%20to%20debate%26quot%3B%20this%20and%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20investigation%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20carried%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSurprised%20That%20MI%20Has%20Moved%20From%20Rohit%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-India%20Star's%20Explosive%20Take%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Was