l.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20as%20well%2C%20he%20captained%20India%20in%20Tests.%20I%20hope%20it%20has%20been%20communicated%20really%20well.%20It%20was%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20but%20it%20happening%20straightaway%20this%20season%2C%20I%20am%20a%20little%20surprised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20was%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20in%20the%20past%20two%20seasons%20and%20in%202022%2C%20he%20even%20led%20them%20to%20the%20title%20on%20their%20debut%20season%20in%20the%20competition.%20However%2C%20the%20all-rounder%20completed%20a%20sensational%20trade%20move%20back%20to%20MI%20ahead%20of%20the%20new%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffer%20also%20wondered%20what%20the%20dynamic%20between%20the%20two%20players%20will%20be%20following%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20MI%20and%20how%20the%20relationship%20will%20alter%20if%20Hardik%20plays%20under%20Rohit's%20leadership%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20if%20he%20(Rohit%20Sharma)%20will%20captain%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20seen.%20Because%2C%20then%20again%20he%20is%20captain%20and%20Hardik%20will%20play%20under%20him.%20So%2C%20how%20does%20that%20happen%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702797000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fk5ijldig_rohit-sharma-806_625x300_16_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsurprised-that-mumbai-indians-has-moved-from-rohit-sharma-ex-india-stars-explosive-take-4685357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wasim%20Jaffer%20was%20surprised%20by%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20decision%20to%20appoint%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20the%20skipper%20ahead%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsurprised-that-mumbai-indians-has-moved-from-rohit-sharma-ex-india-stars-explosive-take-4685357%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsurprised-that-mumbai-indians-has-moved-from-rohit-sharma-ex-india-stars-explosive-take-4685357%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsurprised-that-mumbai-indians-has-moved-from-rohit-sharma-ex-india-stars-explosive-take-4685357%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20Bring%20Nostalgia%20to%20Your%20Turntable%2C%20Two%20Music%20Buffs%20Produce%20Re-Mastered%20Vinyl%20of%20Old%20Bands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123743%2FSavages-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Vinyl%20records%2C%20which%20faded%20away%20in%20the%201980s%20after%20the%20emergence%20of%20cassette%20tapes%20and%20then%20CDs%2C%20are%20enjoying%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20resurgence.%20There%20have%20always%20been%20collectors%20of%20old%20records%20around%2C%20but%20now%20a%20younger%20demographic%20too%20is%20picking%20up%20vinyls%20of%20musicians%20old%20and%20new%20and%20with%20the%20easy%20availability%20of%20turntables%2C%20sales%20are%20picking%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardcore%20collectors%20and%20newbies%20alike%20scour%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Chop%20Bazaar%20and%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20Free%20School%20Street%2C%20looking%20for%20rare%20old%20vinyls%20which%20often%20sell%20at%20prices%20far%20more%20than%20the%20original%20tag.%20Among%20the%20ones%20in%20great%20demand%20are%20very%20rare%20LPs%20and%20singles%20of%20%E2%80%98beat%20groups%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20garage%20bands%20which%20emerged%20in%20India%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20%E2%80%9970s%2C%20playing%20western%20pop%20and%20rock%20music.%20A%20few%20of%20them%20cut%20a%20few%20discs%20of%20their%20original%20compositions%20and%20cover%20songs%20of%20well%20known%20international%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20began%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20sounds%20of%20the%20Beatles%2C%20and%20then%20other%20bands%2C%20heard%20on%20the%20distant%20airwaves%20of%20Voice%20of%20America%20and%20the%20closer%20home%2C%20from%20Radio%20Ceylon%2C%20prompted%20young%20men%20to%20come%20together%20and%20set%20up%20similar%20beat%20groups..%20The%20Trojans%20from%20Bangalore%2C%20the%20Jets%20from%20Bombay%20and%20the%20Flintstones%20from%20Calcutta%20were%20among%20the%20earliest%20to%20be%20formed.%20Their%20equipment%20was%20rudimentary%20%E2%80%93%20some%20used%20homemade%20guitars%20and%20loud%20PA%20amplifiers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20handicap%20of%20not%20freely%20getting%20records%20to%20learn%20the%20chords%20and%20words%2C%20but%20their%20enthusiasm%20was%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201964%2C%20The%20Savages%20were%20formed%20in%20Bombay%20by%20drummer%20Bashir%20Sheikh%2C%20along%20with%20Russel%20Pereira%2C%20Hemant%20Rao%2C%20Prabhakar%20Mundkur%20and%20Ralph%20Pais.%20They%20started%20playing%20the%20live%20music%20circuit%2C%20notably%20at%20night%20clubs%20and%20discos%20like%20Trinca%E2%80%99s%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20at%20colleges%20and%20dances%20in%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pop%20music%20scene%20was%20picking%20up%2C%20and%20a%20new%20generation%20began%20grooving%20at%20these%20sounds%2C%20which%20were%20so%20different%20from%20what%20their%20parents%20had%20heard.%20%3Cem%3EJS%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3EJunior%20Statesman%3C%2Fem%3E)%20magazine%20was%20a%20must%20read%20and%20wearing%20batik%20shirts%20and%20bell-bottoms%20they%20thronged%20to%20music%20competition%20such%20as%20the%20Simla%20Beat%20Contest%2C%20sponsored%20by%20a%20cigarette%20company%2C%20which%20the%20Savages%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20bands%20played%20cover%20songs%2C%20with%20the%20occasional%20original%20number.%20What%20set%20the%20Savages%20apart%20is%20that%20they%20played%20many%20of%20their%20original%20compositions.%20They%20also%20made%20two%20LPs%20and%20many%20singles.%20One%207%E2%80%9D%20single%20featured%20two%20original%20songs%20by%20Hemant%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20%E2%80%98Pain%E2%80%99%20featuring%20budding%20jazz%20singer%20Asha%20Puthli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnusually%2C%20because%20recording%20companies%20were%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20in%20Indian%20bands%2C%20they%20also%20made%20two%20LPs%20(Long%20Playing)%20with%20Polydor%20Records%20India%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Live%E2%80%99%2C%20with%2011%20classic%20tracks%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98Black%20Scorpio%E2%80%99.%20They%20sold%20modestly%20at%20the%20time%20but%20have%20become%20collectors%E2%80%99%20items%20now%2C%20retailing%20online%20for%20up%20to%20500%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Free%20School%20Records%2C%20formed%20by%20two%20record%20collectors%20from%20Kolkata%20%E2%80%94%20Aveek%20Chatterjee%20and%20Rajeev%20Pandey%20%E2%80%94%20have%20reissued%20the%20LP%20%E2%80%98Live%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20limited%20edition%20of%20250%20on%20vinyl.%20Their%20day%20jobs%20are%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20but%20their%20spare%20time%20goes%20in%20republishing%20records%20by%20Indian%20and%20other%20musicians%2C%20old%20and%20new%2C%20of%20which%20they%20have%20already%20issued%20five%20LPs%20on%20vinyl%20and%20one%20on%20CD%2C%20since%202021.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%2C%20200%20copies%20of%20Train%20to%20Calcutta%20by%20folk%20singer%20Susmit%20Bose%2C%20were%20sold%20out%20within%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123906%2FAveek-and-Rajiv_FSSR.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123906%2FAveek-and-Rajiv_FSSR.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%