10.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20October%2C%20the%20actor%20completed%20eight%20years%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20completed%205%20years%20in%20the%20industry%20today%2C%205th%20October%202018%20Loveyatri%20released%20and%20wow%20what%20a%20journey%20it%20has%20been.%20Somebody%20rightly%20said%20that%20your%20first%20film%20is%20always%20going%20to%20be%20special%2C%20hits%20and%20flops%20will%20keep%20happening%20but%20nothing%20comes%20close%20to%20the%20feeling%20of%20working%20on%20your%20first.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Covid%20Variant%20JN.1%20Detected%20In%20Kerala%3A%20All%20About%20The%20Infection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20across%20the%20world%20are%20worried%20about%20a%20new%20COVID-19%20variant%20that%20could%20be%20more%20infectious%20than%20previous%20variants.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-jn-1-the-new-covid-variant-that-has-sparked-worry-among-scientists-4555552%5C%22%3EJN.1%20strain%20of%20coronavirus%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20recently%20been%20detected%20in%20Kerala.%20The%20case%20was%20detected%20in%20an%20RT-PCR-positive%20sample%20from%20Karakulam%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20district%20of%20the%20southern%20state%20on%20December%208.%20The%2079-year-old%20woman%20had%20mild%20symptoms%20of%20Influenza%20Like%20Illness%20(ILI)%20and%20has%20since%20recovered%20from%20Covid.%20This%20variant%20is%20causing%20a%20surge%20in%20infections%20worldwide%20yet%20again%20and%20raising%20alarm%20bells%20among%20health%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Omicron%20subvariant%20known%20as%20BA.2.86%20or%20Pirola%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20COVID%20JN.1%20variant.%20The%20case%20was%20first%20detected%20in%20the%20US%20in%20September%20this%20year.%20Seven%20cases%20of%20the%20specific%20subvariant%20were%20found%20in%20China%20on%20December%2015%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20BA.2.86%20and%20JN.1%20sound%20very%20different%20because%20of%20the%20way%20variants%20are%20named%2C%20there%20is%20only%20a%20single%20change%20between%20JN.1%20and%20BA.2.86%20in%20the%20spike%20protein%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Frespiratory-viruses%2Fwhats-new%2FSARS-CoV-2-variant-JN.1.html%5C%22%3ECDC%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20in%20a%20recent%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spike%20protein%2C%20which%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspike%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20resembles%20small%20spikes%20on%20the%20virus's%20surface%2C%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20virus'%20ability%20to%20infect%20humans.%20According%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20vaccinations%20targeting%20the%20spike%20protein%20of%20a%20virus%20should%20also%20function%20against%20JN.1%20and%20BA.2.86.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Senior%20Consultant%20in%20Chest%20Medicine%20at%20Delhi's%20Ganga%20Ram%20Hospital%2C%20Dr%20Ujjwal%20Prakash%2C%20addressed%20the%20emergence%20of%20this%20variant%20and%20stated%20that%20although%20vigilance%20is%20crucial%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20people%20to%20panic.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20be%20more%20vigilant.%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20there's%20reason%20to%20panic%20or%20do%20anything%20extra%20than%20just%20being%20vigilant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFever%2C%20runny%20nose%2C%20sore%20throat%2C%20headache%2C%20and%2C%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20minor%20gastrointestinal%20problems%20are%20among%20the%20symptoms%20that%20have%20been%20recorded%20in%20patients%20so%20far.%20The%20doctor%20added%20that%20most%20patients%20experience%20mild%20upper%20respiratory%20symptoms%2C%20which%20typically%20improve%20within%20four%20to%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20way%20going%20forward%20is%20testing%20this%20new%20variant%20of%20COVID%20if%20possible%2C%20and%20then%20we%20have%20to%20see%20whether%20they%20have%20COVID%20or%20any%20other%20viral%20infection.%20Symptoms%20are%20almost%20very%20common%20with%20other%20viral%20infections.%20They%20may%20be%20slightly%20more%20severe.%20Some%20patients%20may%20have%20some%20symptoms%20more%20severe%20than%20others%2C%20but%20more%20or%20less%20the%20infection%20is%20just%20like%20any%20other%20viral%20infection%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Prakash%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I%20would%20be%20wise%20enough%20to%20say%20that%20the%20new%20wave%20of%20COVID%20is%20coming.%20It%20may%20just%20pass%20away%20like%20any%20other%20viral%20infection.%20Let's%20keep%20a%20watch%20and%20keep%20our%20fingers%20crossed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20regarding%20the%20emergence%20of%20JN.1.%20He%20advised%20people%20to%20take%20precautions%20by%20wearing%20masks%20and%20undergoing%20testing%20if%20they%20detect%20viral%20infection%20symptoms.%20If%20symptoms%20persist%2C%20individuals%20are%20encouraged%20to%20isolate%20themselves%20from%20the%20general%20public%2C%20the%20doctor%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702794600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1s4qk77g_covid_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-variant-jn-1-detected-in-kerala-all-you-need-to-know-about-the-infection-4689628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20JN.1%20variant%20is%20causing%20a%20surge%20in%20infections%20worldwide%20yet%20again%20and%20raising%20alarm%20bells%20among%20health%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-variant-jn-1-detected-in-kerala-all-you-need-to-know-about-the-infection-4689628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-variant-jn-1-detected-in-kerala