0Bengal%2C%20seeking%20media%20coverage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20now%20found%20burnt%20parts%20of%20the%20phones%20from%20near%20the%20hotel.%20Mahesh%20and%20Lalit%20are%20among%20six%20people%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhanwar%20Lal%2C%20owner%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20said%20it%20was%20only%20when%20police%20came%20to%20him%20that%20he%20realised%20how%20his%20hotel%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20incident%20that%20shocked%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20Mahesh%20Kumawat%20by%20his%20name%2C%20but%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20other%20information%20about%20him.%20Police%20took%20with%20them%20burnt%20parts%20(of%20phones)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20what%20the%20accused%20had%20done%20when%20they%20came%20to%20his%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20yet%20to%20recover%20the%20phone%20of%20Lalit%20Jha%2C%20who%20reportedly%20returned%20to%20Delhi%20after%20destroying%20the%20phones%20and%20was%20arrested%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20massive%20security%20breach%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20attack%20on%20Parliament%2C%20two%20intruders%20--%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%20--%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery.%20They%20then%20went%20from%20desk%20to%20desk%20and%20deployed%20coloured%20smoke%20from%20canisters.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20their%20co-accused%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20raised%20slogans%20outside%20Parliament%20and%20used%20coloured%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20people%20were%20arrested%20soon%20after%20and%20charged%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%20Over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20Mahesh%20Kumawat%20and%20Lalit%20Jha%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20have%20said%20their%20objective%20was%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20unemp