https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fanimal-box-office-collection-day-16-ranbir-kapoor-starrer-crosses-rs-800-crore-worldwide%2Farticleshow%2F106058713.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106058713.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanbir%20Kapoor's%20'Animal'%20continues%20to%20mint%20big%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20crossing%20the%20500%20crore%20mark.%20The%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%2C%20stars%20Bobby%20Deol%2C%20Anil%20Kapoor%2C%20and%20Rashmika%20Mandanna.%20It%20clashed%20with%20Vicky%20Kaushal's%20'Sam%20Bahadur'%2C%20helmed%20by%20Meghna%20Gulzar.%20'Sam%20Bahadur%20'%20is%20a%20historical%20drama%20that%20has%20earned%2071%20crore%20in%2016%20days.%20Por%20'Anima'%2C%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20is%20set%20to%20star%20in%20'Ramayana'%20alongside%20Sai%20Pallavi%2C%20which%20will%20start%20filming%20next%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Royal%20Enfield%20Faces%20Fresh%20Challenge%20From%20Harley%20In%20India's%20Biker%20Paradise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESajneet%20Sandhu%20grew%20up%20riding%20on%20her%20father's%20Royal%20Enfield%20around%20Goa's%20palm-fringed%20roads%2C%20taking%20in%20endless%20beaches%20and%20rice%20paddies%20from%20the%20back%20of%20the%20iconic%20Indian%20motorcycle.%20Now%2043%20and%20inspired%20by%20those%20childhood%20memories%2C%20she%20has%20got%20a%20bike%20of%20her%20own.%20But%20it%20isn't%20like%20her%20dad's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20a%20Royal%20Enfield%20favored%20by%20her%20father%20and%20several%20million%20other%20riders%20in%20India%2C%20Ms%20Sandhu%20opted%20for%20a%20slick%20roadster%20from%20UK-based%20Triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Triumph%20was%20affordable%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'why%20not!'%26quot%3B%20the%20teacher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20choice%20reflects%20a%20shift%20in%20India's%20motorcycle%20scene%2C%20where%20Ms%20Sandhu%20is%20part%20of%20an%20expanding%20middle%20class%20and%20one%20of%20a%20growing%20contingent%20of%20female%20bikers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Triumph%2C%20US%20giant%20Harley-Davidson%20Inc.%20is%20also%20renewing%20efforts%20in%20India%2C%20where%20Royal%20Enfield%20is%20revered%20to%20a%20similar%20extent%20as%20Harley%20is%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20Milwaukee-based%20company%20and%20Triumph%20both%20have%20local%20partners%20so%20they%20can%20produce%20their%20bikes%20more%20cheaply%20in%20the%20world's%20biggest%20two-wheeler%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarley%20initially%20failed%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20India%20and%20pulled%20out%20in%202020%20due%20to%20poor%20sales.%20Its%20imported%20motorcycles%20were%20heavily%20taxed%20and%20not%20designed%20for%20India's%20climate%20and%20potholed%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarley%20launched%20its%20X440%20specifically%20for%20India%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Hero%20MotoCorp%20Ltd.%20in%20Neemrana.%20The%20X440%20starts%20from%20Rs%20239%2C500%20(%242%2C870)%2C%20much%20less%20than%20the%20American%20company's%20cheapest%20imported%20big%20engine%20motorcycle%2C%20the%20Nightster%2C%20which%20costs%20Rs%2010.2%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarley%20says%20it%20has%20taken%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20bookings%20for%20the%20X440%20since%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETriumph's%20Indian%20partner%20Bajaj%20Auto%20Ltd.%20makes%20and%20distributes%20the%20Scrambler%20400X%20and%20Speed%20400%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20262%2C996%20and%20Rs%20233%2C000%2C%20respectively.%20Orders%20for%20those%20began%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20this%20year%20and%20have%20already%20reached%20more%20than%2010%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20Bajaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20suggest%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20manufacture%20more%20affordable%2C%20smaller-engine%20motorcycles%20locally%20is%20paying%20off%20for%20Harley%20and%20Triumph%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20pulling%20closer%20to%20Royal%20Enfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thump%20and%20roar%20of%20Royal%20Enfield's%20Bullet%20motorcycle%20won%20over%20a%20generation%20of%20riders%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20the%20clear%20leader%20in%20small-%20to%20mid-engine%20capacity%20bikes.%20It%20sold%20about%2075%2C140%20motorcycles%20in%20India%20in%20November%2C%20a%20festival-season%20month%20when%20consumer%20spending%20is%20typically%20strongest.%20Royal%20Enfield's%20best-selling%20bike%2C%20the%20Classic%20350%2C%20starts%20from%20Rs%20193%2C080.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople's%20purchasing%20capacity%20has%20improved%20and%20they%20are%20going%20beyond%20their%20city%20commute%20to%20do%20offroading%20and%20leisure%20riding%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul%20Mishra%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20management%20consultancy%20firm%20Kearney.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20also%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20status%20consciousness%2C%20customers%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20with%20bigger%20bikes%20and%20better%20brands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20smaller%2C%20less%20powerful%20motorcycles%20are%20most%20widely%20used%20in%20India%2C%20as%20they%20are%20better%20suited%20to%20lower%20budgets%20and%20the%20need%20to%20navigate%20the%20South%20Asian%20country's%20massive%20and%20congested%20cities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20remote%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%202.25%20million%20two-wheelers%20in%20total%20were%20sold%20nationwide%20in%20November.%20Hero%2C%20Bajaj%2C%20TVS%20Motor%20Co.%20and%20Honda%20are%20the%20top%20sellers%20in%20India%2C%20rolling%20out%20flashy%20advertising%20campaigns%20with%20Bollywood%20stars%20and%20cricketers%20such%20as%20Hrithik%20Roshan%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Sachin%20Tendulkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Enfield%20is%20a%20different%20beast.%20Founded%20in%20the%20UK%20at%20the%20start%20of%20last%20century%20and%20with%20motorcycles%20that%20were%20used%20in%20World%20War%20II%2C%20it%20leans%20more%20on%20an%20enduring%20legacy%20and%20historic%20appeal%20to%20adventure%20seekers.%20Royal%20Enfield%20brand%20ambassadors%20are%20generally%20regular%20people%2C%20not%20multimillionaire%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Enfield%20was%20acquired%20by%20India's%20Eicher%20Motors%20Ltd.%20in%201994.%20The%20bikes%20have%20maintained%20a%20reputation%20for%20rugged%20durability%20that%20suits%20epic%20journeys%20in%20remote%20places%20such%20as%20Leh-Ladakh%20and%20other%20jaw-dropping%20parts%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20and%20enthusiasts%20are%20part%20of%20a%20biking%20fellowship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarley%20and%20Triumph%20share%20some%20of%20those%20traits%2C%20and%20all%20three%20brands%20sell%20associated%20merchandise%2C%20including%20apparel%20and%20biking%20gear%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarley%20imports%20its%20popular%20Fat%20Boy%20and%20Fat%20Bob%20models%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Pan%20America%20tourer%2C%20while%20Triumph%20has%20its%20Tiger%20adventure%20range%20of%20motorcycles%2C%20Bonnevilles%20and%20roadsters%20including%20the%20Speed%20Triple%20and%20Rocket%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sandhu%2C%20Triumph's%20Speed%20400%20was%20most%20appealing%2C%20partly%20thanks%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bsophisticated%20and%20quintessential%20English%26quot%3B%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumeet%20Narang%2C%20an%20executive%20director%20at%20Bajaj%2C%20said%20the%20company%20aims%20to%20more%20than%20double%20Triumph's%20India%20showrooms%20to%20100%20in%20six%20months%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20want%20one%20motorcycle%20to%20cover%20daily%20travels%20as%20well%20as%20road%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20these%20partnerships%2C%20international%20brands%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20in%20products%20which%20are%20designed%20for%20the%20Indian%20market%2C%20and%20that's%20what's%20needed%2C%26quot