E%3Cstrong%3EKolhapur%2FNashik%2FMumbai%2FPune%2FChiplun%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20December%202022%2C%20a%20group%20of%2030-35%20people%20gathered%20for%20a%20rally%20in%20the%20coastal%20town%20of%20Chiplun%20in%20Maharashtra.%20These%20people%20had%20collected%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20infamous%20and%20controversial%20Sanatan%20Sanstha%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20so-called%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20phrase%20used%20to%20describe%20inter-faith%20relationships%20where%20the%20man%20is%20Muslim.%20The%20Shraddha%20Walkar%20murder%2C%20where%20a%20Hindu%20woman%20was%20murdered%20allegedly%20by%20her%20Muslim%20partner%2C%20was%20used%20as%20a%20point%20of%20reference%20to%20amp%20up%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20Chiplun%20police%20for%20raising%20questions%20over%20the%20provocative%20nature%20of%20the%20sloganeering.%20The%20slogans%20by%20the%20Sanatan%20Sanstha%20went%20without%20notice%20while%20requests%20to%20stop%20vitiating%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20the%20town%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdisrupting%20public%20harmony%E2%80%9D.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fusing-love-jihad-as-a-rallying-cry-sanatan-sanstha-attempts-to-communalise-the-konkan%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20same%20incident%20gives%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20Sanathan%20Sanstha%E2%80%99s%20past.%20An%20organisation%20accused%20of%20murdering%20rationalists%20like%20Narendra%20Dabholkar%20and%20Govind%20Pansare%20was%20not%20getting%20the%20attention%20it%20should%20have%20got%20from%20the%20police.%20But%20the%20story%20didn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20had%20only%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20in%20Chiplun%20was%20actually%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20anti-Muslim%20campaign%20prevalent%20throughout%20the%20state%2C%20and%20organised%20at%20scale.%20This%20campaign%20was%20conducted%20under%20a%20new%20entity%20called%20the%20Sakal%20Hindu%20Samaj%20(SHS).%20SHS%20consisted%20of%20a%20spectrum%20of%20Hindutva%20groups%20like%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20Sanatan%20Sanstha%2C%20Hindu%20Janjagruti%20Samiti%2C%20Vishwa%20Shriram%20Sena%2C%20Shri%20Ram%20Pratishthan%20Hindustan%20and%20Durga%20Vahini%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20initial%20half%20of%202023%2C%20a%20startling%20revelation%20emerged%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhate-speech-bjp-anti-muslim-2023%5C%22%3Esubstantial%2029%25%20of%20hate%20speeches%20documented%20nationwide%20were%20concentrated%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Also%2C%20most%20of%20these%20hate%20speeches%20were%20delivered%20during%20the%20SHS%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20promoting%20divisions%20and%20making%20controversial%20speeches%20came%20from%20outside%20the%20state%20too%2C%20able%20to%20come%20together%2C%20under%20the%20SHDS.%20Notable%20speakers%20included%C2%A0%20T.%20Raja%20Singh%2C%20Suresh%20Chavhanke%20and%20Kajal%20Hindustani%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20these%20rallies%20has%20been%20so%20pronounced%20that%20it%20has%20precipitated%20communal%20disturbances%20in%20several%20major%20cities%20across%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20three-part%20docuseries%2C%20we%20dissect%20the%20strands%20of%20this%20political%20narrative%2C%20unveiling%20the%20intricate%20connections%20that%20have%20led%20a%20state%20once%20broadly%20characterised%20by%20harmonious%20coexistence%20to%20a%20creeping%20and%20ominous%20amplification%20of%20actions%2C%20speeches%20and%20public%20articulation%20of%20division%20and%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20I%20of%20the%20series%20introduces%20the%20Sakal%20Hindu%20Samaj%20rallies%2C%20the%20background%20behind%20it%20and%20the%20history%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%20Maharashtra.%20It%20gives%20an%20overview%20of%20the%20past%20three%20decades%20of%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fent9-lRFFsw%3Fsi%3D1RqyuPWHoMAJXqgX%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20II%20focuses%20on%20Kolhapur%20and%20Trimbakeshwar.%20In%20Kolhapur%2C%20on%20June%206%2C%202023%2C%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20350th%20anniversary%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%E2%80%99s%20coronation%2C%20a%20WhatsApp%20video%20extolling%20Tipu%20Sultan%20triggered%20indignation%20among%20certain%20factions.%20While%20a%20protest%20march%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98Sakal%20Hindu%20Samaj%E2%80%99%20on%20June%207%20remained%20peaceful%2C%20the%20following%20day%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvQFLqFI-PgY%5C%22%3EHindu%20groups%20in%20Kolhapur%20turning%20violent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20launching%20stones%20at%20various%20shops%20run%20by%20Muslims.%20In%20Nashik%E2%80%99s%20Trimbakeshwar%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Muslim%20men%20were%20stopped%20at%20the%20entry%20gate%20of%20the%20temple.%20These%20men%20were%20allegedly%20concluding%20a%20%E2%80%9C100-year%20old%20tradition%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20claimed.%20Videos%20of%20this%20event%20went%20viral%20and%20the%20mainstream%20media%20painted%20a%20disturbing%20and%20communal%20picture.%20An%20SIT%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20authenticate%20the%20claims%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20escalating%20situation%20in%20both%20cases%20unveils%20political%20tactics%20aimed%20at%20polarisation%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20which%20may%20be%20ripe%20for%20votes.%20The%20role%20of%20social%20media%20in%20disseminating%20misinformation%20is%20a%20worrisome%20aspect%2C%20especially%20in%20Trimbakeshwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20takes%20a%20deep%20dive%20in%20understanding%20the%20build-up%20and%20aftermath%20of%20both%20these%20major%20communal%20occurrences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FEotmfw-365c%3Fsi%3DuPoaolI-MUaPcsM3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20III%20focuses%20on%20an%20organisation%2C%20Shiv%20Pratishthan%20Hindusthan%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20Manohar%20Kulkarni%2C%20alias%20Sambhaji%20Bhide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhide%20has%20an%20influence%20among%20the%20youth%20in%20Kolhapur%20and%20nearby%20areas.%20His%20affinity%20with%20the%20RSS%20is%20an%20open%20secret.%20Boys%20from%20Shiv%20Pratishthan%20Hindusthan%20were%20accused%20of%20fanning%20the%20riots%20in%20Kolhapur.%20We%20investigate%20this%20case%20and%20shed%20more%20light%20on%20his%20politics%20and%20influence%2C%20by%20talking%20to%20former%20associates%20of%20Bhide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20third%20and%20concluding%20part%20of%20the%20series%20also%20delves%20on%20the%20role%20Marathi%20literature%20and%20films%20have%20had%20in%20developing%20and%20fomenting%20an%20anti-Muslim%20narrative.%20The%20docuseries%20goes%20on%20to%20discuss%20Shiv%20Sena-(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20poses%20the%20question%2C%20if%20its%20newly%20found%20positioning%20in%20INDIA%2C%20as%20an%20anti-BJP%20force%2C%20be%20a%20catalyst%20for%20change%20and%20for%20the%20better%20in%20Maharashtra%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfuYtfdmUltk%3Fsi%3DGF7Tub494yWoqHyM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702789256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17101550%2FTHUMBNAIL.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnaf-rath-in-maharashtra-end-of-reason%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20three-part%20special%20documentary%20series%20on%20the%20spread%20of%20communal%20division%20and%20hate%20in%20Maharashtra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnaf-rath-in-maharashtra-end-of-reason%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Oman%20Discuss%20Gaza%20Conflict%2C%20Back%20Two-State%20Solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20discussed%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20and%20affirmed%20the%20need%20to%20achieve%20a%20two-state%20solution%20with%20the%20visiting%20Omani%20sultan%2C%20Haitham%20bin%20Tariq%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20Arab%20leader%20to%20visit%20India%20since%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20region%20over%20two%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sultan%20is%20the%20first%20Omani%20head%20of%20state%20to%20visit%20India%20in%2026%20years.%20He%20took%20over%20in%202020%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Sultan%20Qaboos%20bin%20Said%20Al%20Said%2C%20who%20had%20last%20visited%20Delhi%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20arrived%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20the%20sultan%20of%20Oman%20held%20formal%20talks%20with%20his%20host%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20media%20briefing%20after%20the%20discussions%2C%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgiven%20the%20developments%20in%20West%20Asia%20in%20terms%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20there%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20multiple%20challenges%20that%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20has%20thrown%20up%2C%20that%20was%20definitely%20an%20important%20element%20of%20discussions%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cshared%20appreciation%20of%20the%20continuing%20challenge%20that%20both%20countries%20face%20from%20the%20emerging%20multiple%20dimensions%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20including%20the%20catastrophic%20humanitarian%20situation%2C%20which%20is%20there%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20secretary%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20were%20committed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20need%20to%20find%20and%20try%20and%20achieve%20a%20two-state%20solution%20as%20a%20way%20forward%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOman%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20moderate%2C%20balancing%20position%20in%20the%20Gulf%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.muscatdaily.com%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Foman-calls-on-palestine-israel-to-exercise-restraint%2F%5C%22%3Einitially%20called%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20both%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20to%20exercise%20restraint%20after%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20attack%20of%20October%207.%20Following%20the%20heavy%20toll%20after%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20counter-strikes%20hit%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20Oman%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Finternational%2520community%2520to%2520conduct%2520an%2520impartial%2520investigation%2520into%2520Israeli%2520actions%2520in%2520the%2520Gaza%2520Strip%5C%22%3Einternational%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Israeli%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20unequivocally%20denounced%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20manifestations%20and%20agreed%20that%20no%20act%20of%20terror%20could%20be%20justified%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20the%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20any%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37458%2FTranscript_of_Special_Briefing_by_Foreign_Secretary_on_the_State_Visit_of_Sultan_of_Oman_to_India_December_16_2023%5C%22%3Ethe%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20underlined%20the%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20for%20all%20countries%20to%20abide%20by%20international%20law%2C%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20all%20nations%2C%20refrain%20from%20interfering%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20and%20resolve%20conflicts%20peacefully%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Oman%20signed%20five%20agreements%20to%20enhance%20collaboration%20in%20information%20technology%2C%20combatting%20financial%20crimes%2C%20cultural%20exchange%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20Hindi%20chair%20under%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Cultural%20Relations%20in%20Oman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20countries%20also%20released%20a%20vision%20document%20which%20lays%20out%20a%20roadmap%20for%20strengthening%20bilateral%20engagement%20across%2010%20key%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20they%20announced%20the%20allocation%20of%20the%20third%20tranche%20amounting%20to%20%24300%20million%20for%20the%20Oman-India%20joint%20investment%20fund%2C%20which%20operates%20as%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Oman%20Investment%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20committed%20to%20expediting%20the%20negotiation%20and%20finalisation%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20economic%20partnership%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20maritime%20security%20cooperation%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20the%20Omani%20port%20of%20Duqm%2C%20Kwatra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20talked%20to%20you%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20both%20leaders%20identified%20humanitarian%20assistance%20and%20disa