a-oman-adopt-vision-document-to-expand-bilateral-cooperation-123121600455_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-oman-adopt-vision-document-to-expand-bilateral-cooperation-123121600455_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-oman-adopt-vision-document-to-expand-bilateral-cooperation-123121600455_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Harassment'%2C%20Pleas%20and%20a%20Petition%20Dismissed%20in%208%20Seconds%3A%20Behind%20Woman%20Civil%20Judge's%20Letter%20to%20CJI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15124522%2Fpexels-sora-shimazaki-5668473.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20will%20to%20live%20anymore.%20I%20have%20been%20rendered%20to%20a%20walking%20corpse%20in%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20There%20is%20no%20purpose%20in%20carrying%20this%20soulless%20and%20lifeless%20body%20around%20anymore.%20There%20is%20no%20purpose%20left%20in%20my%20life.%20Kindly%20permit%20me%20to%20end%20my%20life%20in%20a%20dignified%20way.%20Let%20my%20life%20be%3A%20dismissed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20civil%20judge%20(junior%20division)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20in%20the%20judicial%20circles%20after%20she%20penned%20a%20disturbing%20open%20letter%20to%20the%20topmost%20judge%20in%20the%20country%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20take%20her%20own%20life.%20Her%20grievance%3A%20she%20alleges%20that%20she%20was%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20a%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates%3B%20despite%20her%20following%20the%20proper%20procedure%20and%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20all%20the%20higher%20courts%2C%20she%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20secure%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20letter%2C%20written%20in%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20pain%20and%20despair%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20addressed%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20letter%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2015%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20on%20the%20inquiry%20being%20conducted%20into%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20raised%20by%20the%20woman%20judge.%20The%20CJI%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20respond%20to%20the%20matter%20or%20issue%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20system%20of%20redressal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20one%20particular%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20meet%20the%20district%20judge%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20she%20does%20not%20state%20specific%20instances%20or%20names%20the%20accused%2C%20her%20letter%20provides%20a%20clear%20glimpse%20of%20the%20distressing%20experience%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through%20in%20order%20to%20seek%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20abused%20verbally%20in%20open%20court%20with%20a%20misogynist%20slur%20and%20that%20she%20had%20even%20tried%20to%20kill%20herself%20through%20suicide.%20The%20judge%20reportedly%20endured%20the%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20during%20her%20earlier%20posting%20in%20another%20district%20close%20to%20the%20capital%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20to%20the%20very%20limit.%20I%20have%20been%20treated%20like%20utter%20garbage.%20I%20feel%20like%20an%20unwanted%20insect.%20And%20