ancial%20hardships%20in%20the%20family.%20So%20he%20chose%20to%20stick%20to%20his%20roots%20and%20continue%20the%20family%20business%2C%20unlike%20many%20of%20his%20peers%20who%20migrated%20to%20the%20nearby%20Bengaluru%20city%20for%20odd%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20present-day%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20makers%2C%20steamers%20and%20containers%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20says%20that%20his%20family%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309836%2Ffood-history-of-idli-sambar-roots-in-indonesia-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteam%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20small%20bamboo%20baskets%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20available%20in%20abundance%20in%20our%20village.%20The%20villagers%20make%20and%20sell%20many%20items%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20why%20my%20ancestors%20chose%20to%20utilise%20bamboo%20containers%20to%20make%20idlis%20back%20then.%20Moreover%20using%20bamboo%20makes%20the%20process%20very%20natural.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20unique%20preparation%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20pour%20the%20batter%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20They%20are%20small%20bowl-shaped%20moulds%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20The%20container%20gives%20the%20batter%20a%20perfect%20idli%20shape.%20We%20then%20place%20these%20small%20bamboo%20bowls%20into%20a%20large%20aluminium%20utensil%20using%20bamboo%20sticks%20for%20support.%20Then%20we%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20slowly%20steam%20over%20firewood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fculinaryjourneybynaveen%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0Jhj3eTm6mx67S7cyYDkhocjFkLTESKhrX8GoMGENaQX7v8skATpaV6z67nfotTyxl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVatsala%20informs%20that%20these%20aluminium%20vessels%20%E2%80%94%20around%20two%20feet%20in%20diameter%20%E2%80%94%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20cook%2080%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20a%20time.%20Every%20day%2C%20Vatsala%20and%20his%20team%20of%20six%20helpers%20prepare%20at%20least%20eight%20batches%20of%2080%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20serve%20their%20now%20ever-growing%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20these%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Edistinctive%20from%20other%20cooking%20methods%20is%20their%20rich%20aroma%20and%20flavour.%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20prepare%20the%20batter%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20as%20others.%20But%20the%20whole%20process%20of%20cooking%20it%20in%20bamboo%20baskets%20on%20firewood%20imparts%20a%20rustic%20aroma%20and%20flavour%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20attracted%20thousands%20of%20customers%20including%20YouTubers%2C%20Government%20officials%2C%20ministers%2C%20movie%20celebrities%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20popularity%20of%20Babu%20Hotel%20rose%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20several%20other%20restaurants%20have%20cropped%20up%20around%20his%20village%20that%20are%20offering%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20using%20the%20same%20technique.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20attract%20as%20much%20footfall%20as%20we%20do%20because%20the%20making%20of%20these%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20art.%20Every%20step%20of%20the%20process%20needs%20attention%20to%20detail.%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20my%20family%20do%20this%2C%20so%20my%20learning%20is%20authentic.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20is%20a%20cumbersome%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3