er%20robotic%20arms%2C%20and%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20develop%20different%20types%20of%20arms%20that%20can%20perform%20different%20functions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20main%20aim%20is%20to%20decentralise%20excellence%20wherever%20possible%2C%20make%20the%20technology%20cheaper%20and%20easy%20to%20access%20so%20that%20we%20can%20reach%20every%20rural%20corner%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20their%20approach%20holistic%2C%20he%20opines%20that%20utilising%20technology%20is%20crucial%20for%20advancing%20medicine%20today.%20In%20many%20rural%20areas%2C%20the%20population%20remains%20underprivileged%20in%20terms%20of%20accessing%20the%20best%20possible%20medical%20care%2C%20often%20due%20to%20physicians%E2%80%99%20reluctance%20to%20go%20there%20for%20various%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sudhir%20Srivastava%20with%20his%20surgical%20robot%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sudhir%20Srivastava%20with%20his%20surgical%20robot%3B%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20SS%20Innovations%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E